ironmarch 0.0.1
  • Reference

Iron March Data

Source: R/ironmarch-data.R
im_core_dfs.Rd

Contents of the SQL dump from ironmarch.org, a defunct neo-Nazi/white supremacist message board.

im_core_dfs

im_orig_dfs

im_forums_dfs

im_other_dfs

Format

Each object is a list() of data.table::data.table()s.

Source

https://www.bellingcat.com/resources/how-tos/2019/11/06/massive-white-supremacist-message-board-leak-how-to-access-and-interpret-the-data/

Details

  • Data were acquired via the Bellingcat-linked iron_march_201911_archive.torrent.

Examples

library(data.table)
options(datatable.print.trunc.cols = TRUE)
